sec.p:
RTF interventions varied on two dimensions: the provision of a team reflection session (facilitated or unfacilitated feedback) and the level of feedback reporting (team only or team plus individual clinician). The four intervention combinations were therefore:
facilitated team‐level feedback (Group A);
facilitated team‐ and individual‐level feedback (Group B);
unfacilitated team‐level feedback (Group C); and
unfacilitated team‐ and individual‐level feedback (Group D).
